        "subject": "LU-19929 contrib: Add RISC-V to crash debug tools",
        "message": "LU-19929 contrib: Add RISC-V to crash debug tools\n\nAdd RISC-V64 architecture support to crash module building script.\nThis enables debugging support for Lustre on RISC-V systems.\n\nThe checkstack.pl script already has RISC-V support (added by\nWadim Mueller), but the crash module builder needed updating.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Abdul Halim <abdul.halim@openchip.com>\nChange-Id: I9113d69467d4f63983fefe0718c47d3706a05d9c\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64477\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\n"
